OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780157489
OL,3,CFamily of teenager found dead in lake
OL,4,Cpay tribute 'sensitive and brave' son
OL,6,FThe family of a 17-year-old who was
OL,7,Ffound dead after swimming in a lake
OL,8,Fhave described him as "sensitive,
OL,9,Fbrave, and full of light".
OL,11,FDavid Tita Jr was reported missing
OL,12,Fafter he was last seen in the water in
OL,13,FPick Mere, a lake in Northwich,
OL,14,FCheshire, on Tuesday 26 May.
OL,16,FCheshire Fire and Rescue Service,
OL,17,Falong with specialist Underwater
OL,18,FSearch Teams, carried out the search
OL,19,Fand eventually found the teenager's
OL,20,Fbody later that evening.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
