PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780157489
OL,3,CFamily of teenager found dead in lake
OL,4,Cpay tribute 'sensitive and brave' son
OL,6,FDavid's family said his smile was
OL,7,F"infectious" and he always willing to
OL,8,Fsupport those around him.
OL,10,FPaying tribute, his family said: "No
OL,11,Fwords will ever describe the loss of
OL,12,Four son. He was not only a son, but a
OL,13,Ffriend, a brother and a very
OL,14,Fsupportive force to us, his family and
OL,15,Fthe wider Crewe community.
OL,17,F"David was compassionate, sensitive,
OL,18,Fbrave and full of light. When he
OL,19,Fsmiled, it was as mountains smile to
OL,20,Fsee the spring.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780157489
OL,3,CFamily of teenager found dead in lake
OL,4,Cpay tribute 'sensitive and brave' son
OL,6,F"You were ripped away from having a
OL,7,Ffull and rich life and we were stolen
OL,8,Fthe chance of ever having to see you
OL,9,Fgrow old and have your own children
OL,10,Fand family. This pain in our chests
OL,11,Fwill never leave us and will forever
OL,12,Fbe within our hearts because we love
OL,13,FDavid and that's something no one can
OL,14,Ftake away from us.
OL,16,F"Tonight, and tomorrow and for the
OL,17,Frest of our lives, we will look for
OL,18,Fyou in the stars, the heavens and
OL,19,Fthrough sunsets and remember who you
OL,20,Fwere, until we meet again".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
